                  </persName>
            , ' were married July 10, 1669, being ' both of Stillorgan.'</p>
               <p>Third.</p>
               <p>Licences in the parish of Monckton, and parishes adjoining.</p>
               <p>' Andrew, the son of Ellis and 
               <persName id="t17710911-64-person737">
