               <p>Knight. This comes from the parish of St. James's, London.</p>
               <p>' Baptized the 27th of December, 1713, ' 
               <persName id="t17710911-64-person741">
                  Charles
                   Chadwick
               <interp inst="t17710911-64-person741" type="surname" value="Chadwick"></interp>
